The article is a transcript of remarks made by Vice President Mike Pence at the 10th annual Susan B. Anthony List Gala in Washington, D.C. Pence praises the Susan B. Anthony List as an effective grassroots pro-life organization and thanks them for their support in the 2016 election. He highlights the pro-life policies and personnel choices made by President Trump, including the reinstatement of the Mexico City Policy, the appointment of Neil Gorsuch to the Supreme Court, and the effort to repeal and replace Obamacare. Pence emphasizes the importance of continuing to fight for the sanctity of life and urges the audience to stand up and speak out. He concludes with a message of faith and hope for the future.